data.description:
Welcome to your dream farmhouse! This stunning property offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1861 square feet of living space. 
The kitchen features new stainless-steel appliances and striking granite countertops - a chef's dream come true! 
Outside, you'll find a paradise waiting for you. Relax by the pool with a heated option, complete with a large deck for sunbathing or hosting memorable summer parties. The dog kennel and chicken coop add extra convenience for pet owners or those looking to embrace the homesteading life. Don't forget to pick fresh apples from the apple trees or indulge in the juicy strawberries from your own patch.
The location of this home is ideal for those who love outdoor adventures. With Snowmobile and ATV trails nearby, you'll have endless opportunities to explore the great outdoors. For water enthusiasts, the Black River is just a stone's throw away.
Additional features of this remarkable property include a cozy pellet stove, a convenient shed for extra storage, and a durable metal roof that will last for years to come.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this farmhouse oasis just minutes from the Fort Drum Gate and Airfield.
